Expedition Unknown Series 2: Shangri-La Found
Josh ascends the Himalaya Mountains of Nepal to investigate the legendary Buddhist utopian paradise known as Shangri-La. He investigates some of the 10,000 sky caves carved into the mountains that have never been explored.
"Shangri-La Found," finds the Expedition Unknown crew hiking into even more perilous areas as they continue to explore more caves.
